Compiler option:

g++ -I/usr/include/postgresql/ -I/usr/include/opencv4 -o main main.cpp `pkg-config --cflags gtk4` `pkg-config --libs gtk4` `pkg-config --cflags opencv4` `pkg-config --libs opencv4` -lpq -lpqxx -lportaudio -I/usr/include/portaudio -lb64

Used libs:
GTK4, OpenCV, PostgresSQL, PQXX, PortAudio, b64.

sudo apt-get install libb64-dev (and etc...)
